     div.section
        div.container
            div.row
                div.col-xs-12.col-sm-12.col-lg-6
                    h1.section__title Ohmtech Fire Protection Ltd.
                    p.section__subheader.
                        We offer monthly and annual fire inspection, repairs and troubleshooting of all types of fire alarm panels, fire extinguishers, emergency lights, back flow preventers, sprinkler systems, fire pumps, in-suite inspections of smoke alarm and detectors. #[br]24 hour service to Metro Vancouver and Fraser Valley.
                div.col-xs-12.col-sm-12.col-lg-6
                    form.contact__form.contact__form--splash(method='POST')
                        h4.section__title Get a quote for free
                        div.form-group.row
                            div.col-sm-12
                                input.form-control(type='email')(placeholder='Email')(name='email')
                                label.float-label.input-label Email
                        div.form-group.row
                            div.col-sm-12
                                input.form-control(type='text')(placeholder='Full Name')(name='name')
                                label.float-label.input-label Full Name
                        div.form-group.row
                            div.col-sm-12
                                input.form-control(type='text')(placeholder='Company')(name='company')
                                label.float-label.input-label Company
                        div.form-group.row
                            div.col-sm-12
                                textarea.form-control(rows='3')(placeholder='Your message')(name='message')
                                label.float-label.input-label Your message
                        div.form-group.row
                            div.col-sm-12.text-xs-right
                                button.btn.btn-primary.btn-contact-submit(type='submit') Request a quote
                        div.form__overlay.text-xs-center.hide
                            i.fa.fa-spinner.fa-spin.fa-5x.form__overlay__icon
                            h4.form__overlay__status Sending
     div.section.section--padding.border-top.section-services
        div.container
            div.row
                div.col-xs-12.text-xs-center
                    p.section__subheader  We are a #[span.text-bold fully insured company] that provides service for commercial and residential customers.                    
            div.row
