                    .card.card-block
                        div.card-icon
                            i.fa.fa-circle-thin.fa-2x
                        h4.card-title Sprinkler systems
                        p.card-text Testing, repairs for wet &amp; dry systems;
                .col-xs-10.col-xs-offset-1.col-md-4.col-md-offset-1.section-services__service
                    .card.card-block
                        div.card-icon
                            i.fa.fa-circle-thin.fa-2x
                        h4.card-title Fire hydrants
                        p.card-text Testing &amp; repairs.
            div.row             
                .col-xs-10.col-xs-offset-1.col-md-4.col-md-offset-2.section-services__service
                    .card.card-block
                        div.card-icon
                            i.fa.fa-circle-thin.fa-2x
                        h4.card-title Fire pumps
                        p.card-text Testing &amp; maintenance.
                .col-xs-10.col-xs-offset-1.col-md-4.col-md-offset-1.section-services__service
                    .card.card-block
                        div.card-icon
                            i.fa.fa-circle-thin.fa-2x
                        h4.card-title Backflow preventer
                        p.card-text Testing &amp; repairs.                   
            div.row
                div.col-xs-12.text-xs-center
                    p.section__subheader  Our technicians are #[span.asttbc.text-bold ASTTBC Certified]. We perform inspections according with the #[a(href='http://www.qp.gov.bc.ca/testing/wlap/firecode.htm')(target='_blank') BC Fire Code] and NFPA.
                            
